      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIPPLE LINGER (3) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (20.07) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Has first look at box 3 this time. Has a good record here including four wins. Form from her last run is proving strong. One of the contenders. FEDERAL ESCAPE (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (17.39) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. ARCADIA BELLE (7) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (20.68) last time in a Grade 5 at Grafton. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Has ability and can measure up. TINY DISCO (1) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot at big odds most recently.",
